reviewText:
This is my grandsons favorite video series collection.  He will literally sit and watch these collections for hours
They are great.

We've had this DVD for a while, and it's been great for our kids (ages 7,4 & 2).  Keeps them interested, and it was very worthwhile entertainment with a positive and wholesome message.

We're waiting for the next set to be released, before this one wears out from overuse.
